:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(112869)\">Ether 6:9<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">11. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106841\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106841)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106841)\">Ps. 111:3<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"107292\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 107292)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(107292)\">Isa. 63:1<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">12. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114039\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114039)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114039)\">D&amp;C 56:8<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">13. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111292\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111292)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111292)\">2 Ne. 28:22<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111430\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111430)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111430)\">Jacob 7:4<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">14. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108333\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108333)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108333)\">Mark 7:2<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"109749\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 109749)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(109749)\">Gal. 6:1<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"110392\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 110392)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(110392)\">James 5:16<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114926\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114926)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114926)\">D&amp;C 88:124<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">15. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112173\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 112173)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(112173)\">Alma 34:38<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">16. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108588\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108588)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108588)\">Luke 22:32<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">17. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108892\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108892)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108892)\">John 21:15-17<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">18. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"115667\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 115667)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(115667)\">D&amp;C 112:14<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">19. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"107362\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 107362)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(107362)\">Jer. 23:1<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">20. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112319\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 112319)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(112319)\">Alma 42:27<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">21. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"115835\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 115835)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(115835)\">D&amp;C 121:41<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">22. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112123\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 112123)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(112123)\">Alma 32:43<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116657\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116657)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116657)\">D&amp;C 138:28<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">23. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"115840\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 115840)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(115840)\">D&amp;C 121:43<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">24. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"109446\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 109446)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(109446)\">1 Cor. 3:3<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">25. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"110652\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 110652)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(110652)\">Jude 1:21<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111558\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111558)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111558)\">Mosiah 4:12<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111957\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111957)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111957)\">Alma 13:29<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112753\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 112753)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(112753)\">4 Ne. 1:15<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">26. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108515\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108515)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108515)\">Luke 12:1<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">27. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111567\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111567)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111567)\">Mosiah 4:26<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112180\">